<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/index.php?title=Valhalla&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3" title="Edit section: Physical Characteristics">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Physical_Characteristics">Physical Characteristics</span></h2>
<p>The Valhalla is a long, broad, spiky ship, painted gunmetal gray.
</p>
