<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/index.php?title=Valhalla&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6" title="Edit section: Availability">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Availability"> Availability </span></h2>
<p>The Valhalla does not exist in the vanilla game, but can be added by use of a script.
</p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/index.php?title=Valhalla&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7" title="Edit section: Suggested Roles">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Suggested_Roles"> Suggested Roles</span></h2>
<p>The Valhalla is unique in that it combines the firepower of a heavy <a href="/index.php/M2" title="M2">M2</a> such as the <a href="/index.php/Tyr" title="Tyr">Tyr</a> or <a href="/index.php/Osaka" title="Osaka">Osaka</a> with the fighter capacity of an <a href="/index.php/M1" title="M1">M1 Carrier</a> like the <a href="/index.php/Argon" title="Argon">Argon</a> <a href="/index.php/Colossus" title="Colossus">Colossus</a>.  It would likely serve quite well in either role.
</p>
